name: Christmast Star of Betlehem
description:
Matthew Chapter 2 : 9-10 " 9 - After listening to the king, they went on their way. And behold, the star that they had seen when it rose went before them until it came to rest over the place where the CHILD was. 10 - When they saw the star, they rejoiced exceedingly with great joy."

The christmast star guide the wise man from east to welcome and worship the newborn Jesus that was born in Betlehem.

Merry Christmast and Happy new Year 2022!
God Bless you All!
